ED_Title: Report on the activities of the Office of Internal Oversight Services
ED_DecisionText:
A 

At its 55th (resumed) plenary meeting, on 24 December 2024, the General Assembly took note of the report of the Fifth Committee. (Footnote: A/79/648.)

B [Footnote: Decision 79/550, in section B.6 of the Official Records of the General Assembly, Seventy-ninth Session, Supplement No. 49 (A/79/49), vol. II, becomes decision 79/550 A.] 

At the 63rd plenary meeting, on 11 April 2025, the General Assembly took note of the report of the Fifth Committee10. (Footnote: A/79/648/Add.1).
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/79/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
